{
  "stem": "7238.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was until '41, from '39, if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until or before '41.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We still were moving around in the big ghetto wearing the signs, the yellow badge, and trying our best to be with our families.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could not buy food, but some farmers smuggled in food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you had some money or you had clothing or something, you exchanged for food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then came the holidays.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was, I think, '41.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was the beginning of the Final Solution because, as I mentioned, it was planned so thoroughly to hit the Jews where it hurts the most.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They picked holidays to make the Final Solution.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not all blocks could be taken care of, so the first Rosh Hashanah, we heard about that some blocks of the big ghetto were already empty, because this was what they did.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They sent the Jews off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We still were home, and it was Erev Yom Kippur that we prayed in a private apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I prayed to God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "God, I heard already what happened to the other Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But save my parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I will be a very religious person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I will pray.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I will do good things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But save my parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My prayer was not heard, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because when the holiday of Sukkot came on, this was our turn.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I want also to mention that, at this time, my mother was in a safe bunker in the working place where my brother worked.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was his work?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He collected furnitures from the empty Jewish homes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a big place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
